DESCRIPTION:Learn traditional miniature techniques with artist Mahaveer\, using the cat as your muse while exploring line\, detail\, and colour.\n\nThis hands-on workshop brings together storytelling\, craftsmanship\, and the feline’s enduring charm in Indian art.\n\nThis event is part of the closing weekend celebrations for The Many Lives of the Cat.
